{"title":"大西洋上一枝花  在“支援古巴人民诗歌文艺会”上朗诵","authors":["袁水拍"],"dates":[{"year":1960,"month":4,"day":23}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"大西洋上一枝花"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在“支援古巴人民诗歌文艺会”上朗诵"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"袁水拍"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"加勒比海起风暴，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"白浪里站起了英雄岛，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"昂首小看纸老虎，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"古巴人民志气高！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"挥拳打倒卖国贼，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一脚踢开花旗佬，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为拉丁美洲人民吐气，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为一切殖民地指出了阳关道。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"古巴！古巴！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大西洋上一枝花！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"革命花开香万里，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"敌人咬牙亲人夸！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"路虽远，心相通，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"北京——哈瓦那！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"甘蔗田里的火焰，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就像烧在我们自己的家！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"愿诗人们的语言锻成剑，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"支援你们击落天空的铁老鸦。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"Viva　光荣的革命！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"Viva　英雄的古巴！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"〔注〕Viva　西班牙语“万岁”之意。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}